    "description": "BikeDekho Advisory Limited, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a SEO Specialist for our Raipur operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout BikeDekho Advisory Limited:\nBikeDekho Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Develop and implement category growth strategies\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with BikeDekho Advisory Limited!",
